metadata.name: ETERNAL APE #1
metadata.description: „Eternal Apes“ are here to stay. A new chapter in creation of art was opened in August 2022 though new text-to-image tools. This collection „Eternal Apes“ was created with the help of maybe the first open source AI-image-creation-tool Stable Diffusion, that everybody can run at home. This collection is an homage to the beginning of this new chapter. Let's celebrate, imagine and create.
